import React from 'react';
import {
  Box,
  Container,
  SimpleGrid,
  Heading,
  Text,
  VStack,
  HStack,
  Link,
  Separator
} from '@chakra-ui/react';
import { Link as RouterLink } from 'react-router-dom';
import { FaFacebook, FaTwitter, FaInstagram } from 'react-icons/fa';

const Footer = () => {
  return (
    <Box as="footer" bg="gray.800" color="white" py={8}>
      <Container maxW="container.xl" px={4}>
        <SimpleGrid columns={{ base: 1, md: 4 }} spacing={8}>
          <Box>
            <VStack align="start" spacing={4}>
              <Heading as="h3" size="lg">
                TutorMatch
              </Heading>
              <Text color="gray.300">
                Connecting students with the perfect tutors for their educational journey.
              </Text>
            </VStack>
          </Box>
          
          <Box>
            <VStack align="start" spacing={4}>
              <Heading as="h4" size="md">
                Quick Links
              </Heading>
              <VStack align="start" spacing={2}>
                <Link
                  as={RouterLink}
                  to="/"
                  color="gray.300"
                  _hover={{ color: 'white' }}
                >
                  Home
                </Link>
                <Link
                  as={RouterLink}
                  to="/search"
                  color="gray.300"
                  _hover={{ color: 'white' }}
                >
                  Find Tutors
                </Link>
                <Link
                  as={RouterLink}
                  to="/apply"
                  color="gray.300"
                  _hover={{ color: 'white' }}
                >
                  Become a Tutor
                </Link>
              </VStack>
            </VStack>
          </Box>
          
          <Box>
            <VStack align="start" spacing={4}>
              <Heading as="h4" size="md">
                Resources
              </Heading>
              <VStack align="start" spacing={2}>
                <Link
                  as={RouterLink}
                  to="/blog"
                  color="gray.300"
                  _hover={{ color: 'white' }}
                >
                  Blog
                </Link>
                <Link
                  as={RouterLink}
                  to="/faq"
                  color="gray.300"
                  _hover={{ color: 'white' }}
                >
                  FAQ
                </Link>
                <Link
                  as={RouterLink}
                  to="/support"
                  color="gray.300"
                  _hover={{ color: 'white' }}
                >
                  Support
                </Link>
              </VStack>
            </VStack>
          </Box>
          
          <Box>
            <VStack align="start" spacing={4}>
              <Heading as="h4" size="md">
                Contact
              </Heading>
              <VStack align="start" spacing={2}>
                <Text color="gray.300">Email: info@tutormatch.com</Text>
                <Text color="gray.300">Phone: (555) 123-4567</Text>
                <HStack spacing={4} mt={4}>
                  <Link 
                    href="#" 
                    color="gray.300" 
                    _hover={{ color: 'white' }}
                    fontSize="xl"
                  >
                    <FaFacebook />
                  </Link>
                  <Link 
                    href="#" 
                    color="gray.300" 
                    _hover={{ color: 'white' }}
                    fontSize="xl"
                  >
                    <FaTwitter />
                  </Link>
                  <Link 
                    href="#" 
                    color="gray.300" 
                    _hover={{ color: 'white' }}
                    fontSize="xl"
                  >
                    <FaInstagram />
                  </Link>
                </HStack>
              </VStack>
            </VStack>
          </Box>
        </SimpleGrid>
        
        <Box mt={8} pt={6}>
          <Separator borderColor="gray.700" mb={6} />
          <Text color="gray.300" textAlign="center">
            © {new Date().getFullYear()} TutorMatch. All rights reserved.
          </Text>
        </Box>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Footer;
